quran[55]{c,v,t}:
  82,1,Pamene thambo lidzang’ambika
  82,2,Pamene nyenyezi zidzagwa ndi kubalalitsidwa
  82,3,Ndi pamene nyanja zikuluzikulu zidzaphulika
  82,4,Pamene manda adzatseguka
  82,5,Pamenepo Mzimu uliwonse udzadziwa chimene udatumiza ndi chimene udasiya m’mbuyo
  82,6,oh Iwe munthu! Kodi ndi chiyani chikukunamiza kuti usiye kutsatira malamulo a Ambuye wako Wolemekezeka
  82,7,Amene adakulenga iwe ndi kukukonza kuti uzioneka bwino monga mmene uonekeramu
  82,8,Ndi nkhope ina iliyonse imene idamukondweretsa anakulenga iwe
  82,9,Iyayi! Koma inu mukukana kuti kudzakhala tsiku lachiweruzo
  82,10,Koma pakati panu pali ena amene ali kukuyang’anirani
  82,11,Olemekezeka ndi odziwa kulemba
  82,12,Iwo amadziwa chilichonse chimene mumachita
  82,13,Ndithudi anthu onse angwiro adzakhala mu mtendere
  82,14,"Ndipo, ndithudi, anthu onse oipa adzakhala ku Gahena"
  82,15,Imene iwo adzalowako ndi kulawa malawi ake patsiku lachiweruzo
  82,16,Iwo sadzatha kuthawa ayi
  82,17,Kodi chidzakuuza ndi chiani za tsiku lachiweruzo
  82,18,Tinenanso kodi chidzakuuza ndi chiani za tsiku lachiweruzo
  82,19,Ndi tsiku limene mzimu uliwonse sudzatha kuthandiza wina aliyense ndipo Mulungu yekha ndiye amene adzaweruza
  83,1,Tsoka kwa iwo onse amene amagulitsa malonda awo monyenga
  83,2,Iwo amene amati ena akamawayesera zinthu amafuna kuti zikwanire muyeso wake
  83,3,Koma pamene iwo ayesa kapena awayesera anthu ena amawanyenga
  83,4,Kodi iwo saganiza kuti adzaukitsidwa kwa akufa
  83,5,Patsiku lalikulu
  83,6,Tsiku limene anthu a mitundu yonse adzaima pamaso pa Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse
  83,7,Iyayi! Ndithudi chiwerengero cha anthu onse oipa chili mu Sijjin
  83,8,Kodi udzadziwa bwanji Sijjin ndi chiyani
  83,9,Ili ndi Buku lolembedwa
  83,10,Tsoka pa tsikuli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  83,11,Iwo amene amakana kuti kuli tsiku lachiweruzo
  83,12,Palibe wina amene amalikana tsikuli kupatula munthu wogona m’machimo
  83,13,"Pamene chivumbulutso chathu chinenedwa kwa iye, iye amati: “Izi ndizo nthano za anthu akale.”"
  83,14,Iyayi! Koma m’mitima mwawo ndi mokutidwa ndi zintchito zimene amachita
  83,15,Iyayi! Ndithudi iwo sadzaloledwa kuona Ambuye wawo pa tsikuli
  83,16,Ndipo iwo adzalowa ndi kulawa moto ku Gahena
  83,17,"Ndipo kudzanenedwa kwa iwo kuti: “Chimenechi ndicho chilango chija munkachinena kuti sichidzakhalako.”"
  83,18,Iyayi! Ndithudi chiwerengero cha anthu olungama chimasungidwa mu Illiyyun
  83,19,Kodi mudzadziwa bwanji kuti Illiyin wapamwambayo ndi chiyani
  83,20,"Ndi Al Mutaffifin\t645 Buku lochita kulembedwa"
  83,21,Limene limaonedwa ndi iwo okhawo amene ali kufupi ndi zofuna za Mulungu
  83,22,Ndithudi anthu onse olungama adzakhala ku malo a mtendere
  83,23,Atakhala pa mipando ya wofowofo ndipo ali kuyang’ana uku ndi uku
  83,24,Ndipo udzaona chisangalalo pa nkhope zawo
  83,25,Iwo adzapatsidwa kuti amwe vinyo weniweni amene sanatsegulidwepo
  83,26,"Womaliza wake adzakhala ndi fungo labwino ndipo pachifukwa cha ichi, aleke onse amene afuna kulimbikira kuti alimbike"
  83,27,Wosakanizidwa ndi madzi a Tasnim
  83,28,Kasupe amene anthu odala adzakhala ali kumwa
  83,29,"Ndithudi! Anthu amene amachita zoipa, anali kuwaseka anthu amene anakhulupirira"
  83,30,Ndi kumacheulana iwo akamadutsa pakati pawo
  83,31,Ndipo iwo amati akabwerera kwa anthu awo amabwera ali kunyoza
  83,32,"Ndipo amati akawaona iwo amati: “Ndithudi awa ndiwo anthu osochera.”"
  83,33,Pamene iwo sadalamulidwe kuti akhale owayang’anira
  83,34,Koma pa tsikuli anthu okhulupirira adzaseka anthu osakhulupirira
  83,35,Ali pa mipando yawofowofo ndi kumayang’ana
  83,36,"Kodi anthu osakhulupirira, sanalipidwe mphotho yawo molingana ndi ntchito zawo"